---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="NoLogin Verified Badge"
  description="What is NoLogin Verified? Learn about the badge that certifies tools work without login."
>
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 py-16">
    <!-- Hero -->
    <div class="text-center mb-12">
      <div class="mb-6">
        <img
          src="/badge.svg"
          alt="NoLogin Verified"
          class="inline-block w-40"
        />
      </div>
      <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight mb-3">
        What is NoLogin Verified?
      </h1>
      <p class="text-lg text-neutral-500 max-w-xl mx-auto">
        A badge that certifies a tool's core functionality works without
        creating an account or logging in.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="space-y-8 text-neutral-700 leading-relaxed">
      <!-- For Users -->
      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-neutral-950 mb-3">
          For Users
        </h2>
        <ul class="space-y-2 list-disc list-inside">
          <li>
            Tools with this badge have been <strong>manually reviewed</strong>{' '}
            and verified by our team.
          </li>
          <li>
            The core functionality — the main thing the tool does — is accessible
            without sign-up.
          </li>
          <li>
            We continuously monitor tool availability with automated health
            checks.
          </li>
          <li>
            All verified tools are archived on{' '}
            <a
              href="https://web.archive.org"
              target="_blank"
              rel="noopener noreferrer"
              class="text-blue-600 hover:underline"
            >
              web.archive.org
            </a>{' '}
            for preservation.
          </li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <!-- For Tool Creators -->
      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-neutral-950 mb-3">
          For Tool Creators
        </h2>
        <p class="mb-4">
          If your tool works without login, you can submit it to our directory.
          Once approved, you'll receive the NoLogin Verified badge to display on
          your site.
        </p>
        <div class="bg-neutral-50 border border-neutral-200 rounded-lg p-6">
          <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold text-neutral-950 mb-3">
            How to Get Verified
          </h3>
          <ol class="list-decimal list-inside space-y-2 text-sm">
            <li>
              <a href="/submit" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">
                Submit your tool
              </a>{' '}
              with a description and the core task users can do without login.
            </li>
            <li>Our team reviews the submission (usually within 48 hours).</li>
            <li>
              Once approved, your tool appears in the directory with the
              NoLogin Verified badge.
            </li>
            <li>
              Optionally, add the badge to your site — tools displaying the
              badge get higher visibility in the directory.
            </li>
          </ol>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Badge Display Benefit -->
      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-neutral-950 mb-3">
          Displaying the Badge
        </h2>
        <p>
          Displaying the badge on your site is <strong>optional</strong> and does
          not affect your verified status. However, tools that display the badge
          receive a ranking boost in the directory:
        </p>
        <div class="mt-4 grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-3 gap-4 text-sm">
          <div class="bg-green-50 border border-green-200 rounded-lg p-4 text-center">
            <p class="font-semibold text-green-800 mb-1">SVG Badge</p>
            <p class="text-green-600">+10 rank boost</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-blue-50 border border-blue-200 rounded-lg p-4 text-center">
            <p class="font-semibold text-blue-800 mb-1">Meta / Link</p>
            <p class="text-blue-600">+5 rank boost</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-neutral-50 border border-neutral-200 rounded-lg p-4 text-center">
            <p class="font-semibold text-neutral-800 mb-1">No Badge</p>
            <p class="text-neutral-500">No boost</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>

    <!-- CTA -->
    <div class="text-center mt-12">
      <a href="/submit" class="btn-primary text-base px-8 py-3">
        Submit Your Tool
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
